---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Uses"
  description="The hardware and software I use day to day."
>
  <h1>Uses</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    The hardware and software I actually reach for, not an aspirational list.
  </p>

  <h2>Hardware</h2>
  <dl class="kv">
    <dt>Laptop</dt><dd>MacBook Pro 14" (M1 Pro, 2022)</dd>
    <dt>Display</dt><dd>Dell P2720DC</dd>
    <dt>Keyboard</dt><dd>MoErgo Glove80</dd>
    <dt>Mouse</dt><dd>Logitech MX Ergo</dd>
    <dt>Speakers</dt><dd>ADAM Audio D3V</dd>
  </dl>

  <h2>Software</h2>
  <dl class="kv">
    <dt>Editor</dt><dd>Visual Studio Code</dd>
    <dt>Terminal</dt><dd>Kitty</dd>
  </dl>

  <h2>Stack</h2>
  <dl class="kv">
    <dt>Languages</dt><dd>.NET, Angular, SQL, Python, Swift</dd>
  </dl>

  <h2>Avoid</h2>
  <p>Hardware I regret.</p>

  <div class="table-wrap">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Brand</th>
          <th>Model</th>
          <th>Why</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>ASUS</td>
          <td>ROG Strix X570-I</td>
          <td
            >The most troubled piece of hardware I've ever owned. Never again.</td
          >
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>NZXT</td>
          <td>H1.v1</td>
          <td
            >The case design suffocates the GPU, and one of the bundled AIO
            liquid cooler pipes broke for no reason I could trace.</td
          >
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
